{
  "stem": "16930.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then when we were in Marseilles-- when we were in Dover-- in Le Havre, we went down by train to Marseilles in preparation of going on one of those illegal boats, Aliyah Bet boats to Israel.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I got to Israel-- Do you remember the name of the boat?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I can't think of it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I do-- I-- it's one of the big names, because it had-- these were cargo ships.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "These were cargo ships.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they put in lots and lots of layers of bunks, you know, maybe four or five layers of bunks and full-- where the cargo holds were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people slept on those bunks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And some did go out on deck a little bit.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and it wasn't very comfortable, but it got people there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had bought several of these cargo ships and refitted them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they had some Jews-- some [NON-ENGLISH] Jews, [NON-ENGLISH], who had served in the American navy or British navy during the war who knew how to run ships.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I mean, the ship, you have to know how to do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There has to be a captain and the other people, engineers and whatnot, you know, how to run a boat, run a ship.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So they were-- they had that knowledge and experience and they were doing that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And so when I got to Israel, I joined the Israeli Air Force.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was an illegal [INTERPOSING VOICES].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was still illegal.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- I think the British had already left then, because the British, I believe, left in May, in May '48.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then-- but still they had some kind of control.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, we got in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We got in.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somehow we got in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't know exactly what the-- what the-- we got in.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
